Lines.Comment: Time changes many things, crocbait. I am no exception.
Look at you! King Crocbait! I hope a life of luxury hasn't made you soft...
Now that's the King I remember!
My magic is at your service, my liege.
Varian, the last time I saw you, you were still a pup!
You merely act the wolf... I become the wolf!
We may both be kings, but I lead the pack.
Easily said... but NOT easily proven.
Varian... I hope that temper of yours won't be a liability.
It gladdens my heart to see you once more, friend.
